title: California right-to-die bill clears finance committee, heads to Assembly floor
text:
08 California right-to-die bill clears finance committee, heads to Assembly floor 
San Jose Mercury News: SACRAMENTO -- Legislation that would allow terminally ill Californians to end their lives with help from a doctor cleared an Assembly committee Friday after a low-key hearing on one of the year's most controversial proposals.
